br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXea%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ae1f072e\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記得Check verify email</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊係侵侵啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ec1bf8b41acb57b7aa5d1290129b2573f9f1693","tid":1571082,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"但佢block 撚哂入黎同出去d路"}]}